    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    1.41
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   = 0.707
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>Perimeter</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>P</var>
   = 4 ·
   <var>a</var>
   = 4 · 1 = 4
  </span>
  m
 </p>
 <p>Second moments of area</p>
 <p>
  <i>I</i>
  <sub>z</sub>
  =
  <span class="eq">
